parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The electrical system failure can cause the 12V battery to drain, leading to a dead battery, which can leave the driver stranded, and in some cases, may cause safety hazards such as a failed horn or instrument panel.
symptoms: The 12V battery drains excessively
the vehicle won't start
the horn stops working
the instrument panel fails
the vehicle experiences a parasitic drain
the battery meter does not reflect the true available storage.

symptoms: The 12V battery drains excessively
the vehicle won't start

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hybrid/power battery can cause the vehicle to malfunction, leading to safety hazards such as a failed electrical system, and in some cases, may cause the vehicle to be unable to operate.
symptoms: The vehicle malfunctions
the electrical system fails
the vehicle is unable to operate
the battery fails to charge
the vehicle experiences inconsistent charging rates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to access the charging port due to a faulty door latch can prevent owners from charging their vehicles, leading to reduced vehicle functionality and potential stranding.
symptoms: The push door to the charging port locks and cannot be opened
the door sometimes unlocks after repeatedly pressing the unlock button
difficulty or inability to access the charging port.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A design flaw or malfunctioning latch can cause the charging port door to lock, restricting access to the charging port and hindering vehicle charging.
symptoms: The charging port door latch is faulty
the door locks unexpectedly
difficulty or inability to access the charging port.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden unintended acceleration can cause the vehicle to accelerate rapidly, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates rapidly without input from the driver
the vehicle continues to accelerate despite braking
the vehicle jumps or surges forward
the collision warning system fails to alert the driver.
